flowchart TD
    A[Exchange market data\nREST / websocket poller] --> B[Normalizer + local market store]
    B --> C[Rolling feature context]
    C --> D[LONG / SHORT model inference]
    D --> E[Candidate ranking + calibration]
    E --> F[Risk engine\nslots, regimes, fees, stop distance]
    F --> G{Admissible?}
    G -- No --> H[Decision log]
    G -- Yes --> I[Paper/live position manager]
    I --> J[Open/closed trade ledger]
    J --> K[Reconciliation checks]
    K --> L[Heartbeat + monitoring alerts]

    M[Private model artifacts] -. not published .-> D
    N[Private exchange adapter] -. not published .-> A
    O[Private credentials] -. never published .-> A
